title: (Mon Early Bird) Lunchbox's Gross Restaurant Complaint + Crazy Pregnancy Story + Mailbag: Listener Doesn't Want His Son To Get a Tattoo
itunes:title: (Mon Early Bird) Lunchbox's Gross Restaurant Complaint + Crazy Pregnancy Story + Mailbag: Listener Doesn't Want His Son To Get a Tattoo
description:
Lunchbox saw something gross happen at a restaurant, so he called them to complain. Plus, we hear a crazy pregnancy story from a woman who had no idea she was pregnant until the baby's head came out. We go around the room to see if you believe it. We open the mailbag and help a listener who doesn't want their 18-year-old son to get a tattoo just yet and needs advice on how to get him to think and wait on it.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
